  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to collect data on the prevalence and clinical significance of
      elevated cardiac troponin in a large registry of unselected patients with atrial fibrillation
      presenting to an emergency department.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
